Detailed Description

Type define for a Mass Storage class Command Block Wrapper, used to wrap SCSI commands for transport over the USB bulk endpoints to the device.

Field Documentation

uint32_t CommandBlockWrapper_t::DataTransferLength

Length of data to transfer, following the CBW

uint8_t CommandBlockWrapper_t::Flags

Block flags, equal to one of the COMMAND_DIRECTION_DATA_* macros

Command block signature, always equal to CBW_SIGNATURE
